# Cross-origin isolation so SharedArrayBuffer is available in production (enables
# the multi-threaded AI). Netlify / Cloudflare Pages read this file verbatim; for
# other hosts replicate these two headers on the HTML document response. Without
# them the game falls back to single-threaded AI (still fully playable).
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
